{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">KEY FEATURES:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">New setting: a puppet show.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Blends distinct horror styles. (Tim Burton / Junji Ito / A24 films)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">New puzzle mechanics involving rotating and zooming both individual props and the entire scene.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The soundtrack blends with your actions, creating a dark fairy tale atmosphere.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You'll feel like a spectator of the show, another main character in the game. And the evil doesn't chase the puppet, as it usually does in platformers, it chases you.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1974230/extras/616devblood.gif?t=1738774866\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">GAMEPLAY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Puzzles: They are the core of the game. You can rotate, move, and even flip the stage or individual props.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Boss Battles: You\u2019ll face off against bosses like a Ferris wheel, pipes, and, for example, a giant jaw.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game doesn't hold your hand. You'll have to re-analyze the logic in each room.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1974230/extras/616.2.gif?t=1738774866\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">HORROR</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game's storytelling style shifts as the plot progresses, moving from a Tim Burton-esque fairy tale to a horror style like Junji Ito's.  It feels like a collaborative horror animated film by these two masters. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You'll have to deal with 